  "title": "Sales Executive – Corporate Services",
  "description": "<p><strong>Services Scope:</strong></p><p>Company incorporation, corporate secretarial services, and market entry consultancy.<br /><br /><strong>Key Responsibilities:</strong></p><ul><li><p>Generate B2B leads through social media marketing, online platforms and networking</p></li><li><p>Manage and grow company social media channels to attract overseas businesses entering Singapore</p></li><li><p>Develop partnerships with overseas agents and channel partners</p></li><li><p>Conduct cold calls, arrange meetings and present company services to decision makers</p></li><li><p>Build and maintain corporate client relationships</p></li><li><p>Achieve monthly sales targets and support client onboarding</p></li></ul><p><strong>Requirements:</strong></p><ul><li><p>Sales / Business Development / Marketing experience preferred</p></li><li><p>Familiar with social media and digital marketing</p></li><li><p>Strong communication and negotiation skills</p></li><li><p>Independent, self-motivated and target-driven</p></li></ul><p><strong>Others:</strong><br />High commission structure, flexible working arrangement</p>",
